nt-weight: bold;\">Reset</button>\n\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"hide-large\">\n                    <div w3-include-html=\"fixed_applets_message.html\"></div>\n                </div>\n\n               \n\n                <div class=\"practice\">\n                    <p><strong>Exercise:</strong> Find the velocity field of the flow produced\n                        by a source of strength @@math:40:3cbc5a@@ in a uniform flow at speed @@math:41:f67ade@@ in the\n                        @@math:42:114ae0@@-direction.</p>\n                </div>\n\n\n                <br />\n\n            </div>\n\n\n        </article>\n    </main>\n\n    <a href=\"flow_around_circle.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">\n        <p class=\"nextPage\">Uniform flow around circle <i class=\"fa-solid fa-angles-right\"></i></p>\n    </a>\n    @@verbatim:2:e2a760@@\n\n</section>"
